Radiation therapy uses high-energy beams, such as X-rays or protons, to kill tumor cells #BrainTumor http://t.co/dtUSgQy74Z
External beam radiation can be applied to your entire brain (whole-brain radiation). #BrainTumor
Whole-brain radiation is most often used to treat cancer that has spread to the brain from some other part of the body. #BrainTumor
Chemotherapy uses drugs to kill tumor cells #BrainTumor http://t.co/dtUSgQy74Z
Chemotherapy drugs can be taken orally in pill form or injected into a vein #BrainTumor http://t.co/dtUSgQy74Z
